---
title: Harissa and Honey-Glazed Chicken Thighs with Almond Couscous and Garlic Sauce
description: Smoky, fragrant and gently spicy harissa meets sweet and sticky honey to create bold, caramelized flavour in this succulent chicken dish. A creamy garlic-lemon sauce brings balance and dimension to both the chicken and couscous.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/harissa-and-honey-glazed-chicken-thighs-25407054.jpg
